channel.title: Ijabah Cinta
channel.desc: Cinta is a beautiful, soleha, and cheerful girl. One day, Cinta met Biru, a handsome, wealthy young man from Jakarta. Unexpectedly, Cinta & Biru fell in love with each other, leading to marriage. However, after the marriage Cinta experienced a terrible thing and was left by Biru. Cinta was deeply traumatized, and what was to become of her life.
